S.FORM: Joan-Enric Vives i Sicília I 1949 a miheca saka 7 folad saka 24 a romi'ad masofoc ci Joan-Enric Vives i Sicília, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Andorra anini i ci Joan-Enric Vives i Sicília, patirengan a romi'ad i 2003 a miheca saka 5 folad saka 12 a romi'ad.
